OL,3,CQuadruple killer allegedly attacks
OL,4,Cinmate with hammer at high-security
OL,5,Cprison
OL,7,FA convicted killer who murdered his
OL,8,Fpregnant partner and three children
OL,9,Fhas allegedly attacked a fellow
OL,10,Fprisoner, according to press reports.
OL,12,Fafter killing Terri Harris, her
OL,13,Fchildren, John Paul and Lacey Bennett,
OL,14,Fand Lacey's friend, Connie Gent, in
OL,15,FKillamarsh, Derbyshire, on September
OL,16,F19, 2021.
OL,18,FHe pleaded guilty to murder after
OL,19,Fattacking the four victims with a claw
OL,20,Fhammer. He also pleaded guilty to
OL,21,Fraping 11-year-old Lacey.
