OL,7,FIt's been reported that Bendall has
OL,8,Fattacked a fellow inmate in the head
OL,9,Fwith a claw hammer during a jail
OL,10,Fworkshop at Frankland Prison in Durham.
OL,12,FThe victim is currently in hospital
OL,13,Fand is alleged to be in a life-
OL,14,Fthreatening condition.
OL,16,FDurham Constabulary confirmed that it
OL,17,Fwas investigating the incident.
